<item>
            <title>[LU-14023] sanity test_56oc: @@@@@@ FAIL: &apos;/usr/bin/lfs find /mnt/lustre/d56oc.sanity ! -neweram /mnt/lustre/f56oc.sanity.negnewer.am&apos; wrong: found 12, expected 16</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14023</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Vladimir Saveliev &amp;lt;c17830@cray.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/6bf04d76-1386-4340-9901-b90a0ff7e8c5&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/6bf04d76-1386-4340-9901-b90a0ff7e8c5&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_56oc failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&apos;/usr/bin/lfs find /mnt/lustre/d56oc.sanity ! -neweram /mnt/lustre/f56oc.sanity.negnewer.am&apos; wrong: found 12, expected 16
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Other instances:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/f4481298-9466-480f-81c3-f1ad681000d3&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/f4481298-9466-480f-81c3-f1ad681000d3&lt;/a&gt; - this has most similar signature:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;/usr/bin/lfs find /mnt/lustre/d56oc.sanity -neweram /mnt/lustre/f56oc.sanity.newer.am ! -neweram /mnt/lustre/f56oc.sanity.negnewer.am&apos; wrong: found 12, expected 16
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are many other failures of sanity test_56oc. The most frequently they have:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;/usr/bin/lfs find /mnt/lustre/d56oc.sanity -newerbt 2020-10-02 03:25:39&apos; wrong: found 0, expected 16
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13665&quot; title=&quot;master-2.12 interop: sanity multiple failures&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-13665&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-13665&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; attributes these failures to interop, however in &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/6bf04d76-1386-4340-9901-b90a0ff7e8c5&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/6bf04d76-1386-4340-9901-b90a0ff7e8c5&lt;/a&gt; there were 2.13.55.1 on clients and servers,&lt;br/&gt;
in &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/f4481298-9466-480f-81c3-f1ad681000d3&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/f4481298-9466-480f-81c3-f1ad681000d3&lt;/a&gt; - 2.13.56.1 everywhere.&lt;/p&gt;






&lt;p&gt;VVVVVVV DO NOT REMOVE LINES BELOW, Added by Maloo for auto-association VVVVVVV&lt;br/&gt;
sanity test_56oc - &apos;/usr/bin/lfs find /mnt/lustre/d56oc.sanity ! -neweram /mnt/lustre/f56oc.sanity.negnewer.am&apos; wrong: found 12, expected 16&lt;/p&gt;</description>
